title: Episode 37 "Phone Time"
itunes:title: Episode 37 "Phone Time"
description:
N.O.R.E. and DJ EFN are the Drink Champs. In this episode the guys randomly call some of their hip hop colleagues and chop it up with Lloyd Banks, B Real of Cypress Hill, Fat Joe, Lyor Cohen, Tech N9ne and more. Also Eddie the Ass eater's video gets leaked and Twin makes a speech, all this and more on episode 37! --- Support this podcast: https://anchor.fm/drinkchamps/support
